  "texts": [
    "The model then packs the transformed input tokens into a matrix X that the decoder uses during training and inference.",
    "During training, the model learns the parameters of its ANN in the decoder stack to maximize the probability of correctly predicting the next token in the input sequence.",
    "After training, the model has learned the underlying phenomenon that produced all the text corpus used to train it.",
    "That is, the model learned general knowledge from the training examples to generate responses that are consistent with human understanding, within the context of the prompt.",
    "During inference, the model gives the impression that it understands the syntax, semantics, and context of a prompt sufficiently well to produce a sensible and informative response."
  ],
